Good deal on the special edition of this set. My wife likes to collect them. They did a good job to restore it to the way it was seen in Japan.
Great classic series, but wish they wouldn't have broken the series into so many sets.  worth to collect if you're fan of the old series.

This set is available at a great price, and includes an artbox, bluray case with 3 discs and 23 episodes, art card, and a booklet with episode summaries of the included episodes. Video is remastered and in the original 4:3 aspect ratio. Everything looks and sounds great, and the set is more compact than the old thinpak dvd release, which had no episode guide. It was worth upgrading

We are madly in love with this series in my houshold, from my daughter to the cat.  This is a great all ages show.  Lots of humor a little lo brow at times but Ranma is so likeable you really feel for the guy!
Having this series of anime on blu ray makes a huge difference in quality of the discs as well as sound and picture quality of this show bottom line is blu Ray is better if you can afford it
